               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17900424-1-cd2" type="crimeDate">26th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900424-1-off1 t17900424-1-cd2"></join> last, one black gelding, value 10 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17900424-1-victim6" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Moffatt
